112
00:10:00,788 --> 00:10:04,448
but damn, even I didn’t expect this.

113
00:10:12,578 --> 00:10:14,678
You’re not in control anymore

114
00:10:15,578 --> 00:10:18,967
If I don’t see that money hit my account soon

115
00:10:18,967 --> 00:10:21,126
you know what’ll happen

116
00:10:21,126 --> 00:10:23,340
A respected university lecturer

117
00:10:23,340 --> 00:10:26,131
married just to stay in the closet

118
00:10:26,131 --> 00:10:29,468
hitting on male students

119
00:10:29,468 --> 00:10:32,886
one of whom is your future brother-in-law?

120
00:10:32,886 --> 00:10:38,368
Wonder what your parents, your sister, would think.

121
00:10:40,972 --> 00:10:42,709
Do whatever you want.
